urns `true`, if there are no\nanchor references restricting the search, or there is an anchor\nreferences `ref` s.t. `ref` matches `proof`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/ForallProp.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.checkAnchorRefsEMatchTheoremProof","kind":"def","line":78,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.checkAnchorRefsEMatchTheoremProof","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/9d4ad1273f6cea397c3066c2c83062a4410d16bf/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/ForallProp.lean#L78-L86"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/ForallProp.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.propagateForallPropUp\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">propagateForallPropUp</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM\">GoalM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `parent` is a projection-application `proj_i c`,\ncheck whether the root of the equivalence class containing `c` is a constructor-application `ctor ... a_i ...`.\nIf so, internalize the term `proj_i (ctor ... a_i ...)` and add the equality `proj_i (ctor ... a_i ...) = a_i`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/ForallProp.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.propagateForallPropUp","kind":"def","line":21,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.propagateForallPropUp","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/9d4ad1273f6cea397c3066c2c83062a4410d16bf/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/ForallProp.lean#L21-L58"}}],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Types","Init.Grind.Propagator","Init.Simproc","Init.Grind.Norm","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.PropagatorAttr","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Propagate","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Internalize","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Simp","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Anchor","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.EqResolution","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.SynthInstance"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.ForallProp"}